## Exemplo com SDK C#

<Tabs items={[{"label":"Obter perfil","content":"<pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">    var userResult = await client.Users.GetCurrentUserAsync();\n\n    if (userResult.IsSuccess)\n    {\n        var user = userResult.Value;\n        Console.WriteLine($&quot;Name: {user.Name}&quot;);\n        Console.WriteLine($&quot;Email: {user.Email}&quot;);\n        Console.WriteLine($&quot;Theme: {user.Preferences.Theme}&quot;);\n        Console.WriteLine($&quot;Timezone: {user.Preferences.Timezone}&quot;);\n    }\n</code></pre>"},{"label":"Atualizar perfil","content":"<pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">    var updateResult = await client.Users.UpdateCurrentUserAsync(\n        new UpdateUserRequest(\n            Name: &quot;John D. Doe&quot;,\n            AvatarUrl: &quot;https://example.com/new-avatar.jpg&quot;\n        )\n    );\n\n    if (updateResult.IsSuccess)\n    {\n        Console.WriteLine(&quot;Profile updated!&quot;);\n    }\n</code></pre>"},{"label":"Atualizar preferências","content":"<pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">    var prefsResult = await client.Users.UpdatePreferencesAsync(\n        new UpdateUserPreferencesRequest(\n            Theme: &quot;dark&quot;,\n            Timezone: &quot;America/Los_Angeles&quot;,\n            NotificationsEnabled: false,\n            DefaultRegion: &quot;us-west-1&quot;\n        )\n    );\n\n    if (prefsResult.IsSuccess)\n    {\n        Console.WriteLine(&quot;Preferences updated!&quot;);\n    }\n</code></pre>"}]} />

---

## Campos do perfil

| Field | Type | Editable | Description |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| `userId` | string | No | Unique user identifier |
| `email` | string | No | Account email (contact support to change) |
| `name` | string | Yes | Display name |
| `avatarUrl` | string | Yes | Profile picture URL |
| `role` | string | No | Role in current organization |
| `status` | string | No | Account status |
| `preferences` | object | Yes | User preferences |
| `lastLoginAt` | datetime | No | Last login timestamp |
| `createdAt` | datetime | No | Account creation date |
| `updatedAt` | datetime | No | Last update timestamp |

---

## Valores de status do usuário

| Status | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `active` | Account is fully operational |
| `pending` | Email verification pending |
| `suspended` | Account is suspended |
| `deleted` | Account has been deleted |

